kubectl version                                                             Say your kubernates version

kubectl get deployments                                                     Getting your kubernate deployments

kubectl get pods                                                            Getting your pods on kubernates

kubectl get namespace                                                       Getting namespaces

kubectl get storageclass                                                    Getting storage classes

kubectl get pvc                                                             Getting persistence volumes

kubectl apply -f <YOUR CUBERNATES YAML FILE>                                Apply your docker container to kubernates

kubectl delete deployment <YOUR DEPLOYMENT NAME>                            Deleting your deployment

kubectl rollout restart deployment platforms-depl                           Restart deployment
